### Get all reviews 
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json



### Get a single review
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/3c62d98f-cabf-4c2b-9d0f-7c1b32c5de2c
Content-Type: application/json



### Get Reviews by Car
GET http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/car/75e07434-394e-4c93-8b1d-66ab1b512345
