### Add a New Review
POST http://localhost:3000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "9c9485dc-16a5-4d72-8d2e-034e43f15289",
  "carId": "75e07434-394e-4c93-8b1d-66ab1b512345",
  "content": "The car was amazing! Smooth ride.",
  "rating": 5
}



